00:15:44,260 --> 00:15:44,980
Anyway,

279
00:15:45,690 --> 00:15:47,330
they already have the Rama Vessel

280
00:15:47,330 --> 00:15:49,150
and three pieces of the Rama Heavenly Ice.

281
00:15:49,150 --> 00:15:50,440
They will try to get

282
00:15:50,860 --> 00:15:52,040
the one in our hands.

283
00:16:02,030 --> 00:16:02,830
Young Master.

284
00:16:03,300 --> 00:16:05,020
The Master of the Tianji Mountain Manor sent a letter,

285
00:16:05,020 --> 00:16:07,620
asking you to return to the Manor immediately.

286
00:16:10,870 --> 00:16:11,530
Li Lianhua.

287
00:16:11,930 --> 00:16:14,330
My mother asked me to take you back to the Tianji Mountain Manor.

288
00:16:14,330 --> 00:16:16,020
You said you gave the ice shard to your mother.

289
00:16:16,020 --> 00:16:17,810
Is there something wrong?

290
00:16:26,350 --> 00:16:27,130
You didn't find

291
00:16:27,130 --> 00:16:30,330
the Rama Heavenly Ice in the hands of Four-faced Qingzun?

292
00:16:30,980 --> 00:16:32,800
At that time, Four-faced Qingzun was seriously injured

293
00:16:32,800 --> 00:16:33,860
and died in prison.

294
00:16:34,190 --> 00:16:35,920
He left the Rama Heavenly Ice to his wife,

295
00:16:35,920 --> 00:16:37,200
Liangyi Fairy.

296
00:16:37,620 --> 00:16:39,010
I didn't know about it until I broke into the prison.

297
00:16:39,010 --> 00:16:40,180
After Four-faced Qingzun died,

298
00:16:40,180 --> 00:16:42,510
Liangyi Fairy also died of hunger strike.

299
00:16:42,780 --> 00:16:43,750
But strangely,

300
00:16:43,990 --> 00:16:49,660
[Foreworld Forever]

301
00:16:44,400 --> 00:16:46,940
I found the whereabouts of Liangyi Fairy after her death

302
00:16:46,940 --> 00:16:49,600
in the residence of Mr. Pi who guards the prison.

303
00:16:52,490 --> 00:16:53,910
She is still alive?

304
00:16:54,630 --> 00:16:56,900
Where do you think she'd be hiding

305
00:16:57,240 --> 00:16:58,770
with the Rama Heavenly Ice?

306
00:16:59,160 --> 00:17:01,230
Mr. Pi comes from the Tianji Hall.

307
00:17:01,780 --> 00:17:04,510
We're going to the Tianji Mountain Manor anyway.

308
00:17:04,520 --> 00:17:05,450
We are on the way.

309
00:17:24,700 --> 00:17:25,329
Saintess.

310
00:17:26,950 --> 00:17:28,339
You are too slow.

311
00:17:30,630 --> 00:17:33,230
Saintess, what happened?

312
00:17:39,619 --> 00:17:40,540
Is it scary?

313
00:17:47,140 --> 00:17:49,340
Even if I have a few more scars on my face,

314
00:17:50,080 --> 00:17:51,330
he doesn't care.

315
00:17:52,640 --> 00:17:54,010
All men in the world

316
00:17:54,040 --> 00:17:55,590
would die for me.

317
00:17:56,670 --> 00:17:59,390
I spent ten years of my life on him,

318
00:17:59,420 --> 00:18:01,420
but still failed to make him like me.

319
00:18:02,060 --> 00:18:03,660
He doesn't care about my love

320
00:18:03,980 --> 00:18:05,380
or my hatred.

321
00:18:07,380 --> 00:18:09,760
Even though he's indifferent to me,

322
00:18:10,380 --> 00:18:11,470
I still like him.

323
00:18:13,940 --> 00:18:16,710
Are our men ready?

324
00:18:18,420 --> 00:18:19,810
Thanks to you,

325
00:18:19,830 --> 00:18:22,130
you've cultivated your own forces over the years.

326
00:18:22,130 --> 00:18:23,860
The Yulongniuma Gang is ready.

327
00:18:24,610 --> 00:18:25,870
We are waiting for you.

328
00:18:26,540 --> 00:18:27,540
Di Feisheng.

329
00:18:28,770 --> 00:18:31,970
I will always remember the love and hatred over the years.

330
00:18:32,420 --> 00:18:33,220
We should

331
00:18:34,190 --> 00:18:35,990
play the game in a different way.

332
00:18:42,810 --> 00:18:45,890
[Tianji Mountain Manor]

333
00:18:44,420 --> 00:18:46,060
You asked me to come back in such a hurry,

334
00:18:46,060 --> 00:18:47,920
saying there's something very important to do,

335
00:18:47,920 --> 00:18:48,650
and it's just

336
00:18:49,360 --> 00:18:50,430
my Auntie's wedding.

337
00:18:50,430 --> 00:18:51,230
What's wrong?

338
00:18:51,340 --> 00:18:51,840
Can't I?

339
00:18:52,130 --> 00:18:53,190
Stop complaining.

340
00:18:56,660 --> 00:18:57,450
Mr. Li.

341
00:18:57,890 --> 00:18:59,200
You're too late.

342
00:18:59,690 --> 00:19:00,530
You've missed

343
00:19:00,920 --> 00:19:01,680
Xiaofeng.

344
00:19:02,020 --> 00:19:02,810
Master He,

345
00:19:02,980 --> 00:19:04,580
please stop making fun of me.

346
00:19:06,800 --> 00:19:08,660
Auntie's marriage is too sudden.

347
00:19:11,290 --> 00:19:13,390
I know her thoughts.

348
00:19:13,930 --> 00:19:14,700
In her heart,

349
00:19:14,980 --> 00:19:16,780
she still can't let go of Mr. Li,

350
00:19:17,240 --> 00:19:19,640
but she knows that she has no hope with Mr. Li

351
00:19:19,700 --> 00:19:20,940
and is disheartened.

352
00:19:21,790 --> 00:19:23,710
Don't take it personally.

353
00:19:24,190 --> 00:19:25,950
She's just that kind of person,

354
00:19:26,450 --> 00:19:27,460
emotional

355
00:19:27,640 --> 00:19:28,950
and capricious.

356
00:19:29,540 --> 00:19:30,340
Well, you see,

357
00:19:30,350 --> 00:19:33,460
a few days ago, she picked up an injured man at the foot of the mountain.

358
00:19:33,460 --> 00:19:34,260
You know what?

359
00:19:34,320 --> 00:19:36,250
This young man is really handsome.

360
00:19:36,410 --> 00:19:36,850
And now

361
00:19:37,260 --> 00:19:39,920
she's fallen in love with him after taking care of him for a few days.

362
00:19:39,920 --> 00:19:41,560
She married a man just like that?

363
00:19:41,560 --> 00:19:42,490
That's too fast.

364
00:19:43,220 --> 00:19:43,980
It's indeed

365
00:19:44,010 --> 00:19:45,240
a little hasty.

366
00:19:45,590 --> 00:19:47,820
But they are already

367
00:19:47,850 --> 00:19:48,980
in love with each other.

368
00:19:48,980 --> 00:19:51,840
They just wanted to get married as soon as possible.

369
00:19:51,840 --> 00:19:54,290
At first I wanted to invite you to the wedding,

370
00:19:54,290 --> 00:19:56,780
but as soon as Xiaofeng heard that Mr. Li was coming,

371
00:19:56,780 --> 00:19:59,110
she insisted on getting the wedding done.

372
00:19:59,420 --> 00:20:00,380
In her heart,

373
00:20:00,580 --> 00:20:02,250
she still cares about Mr. Li.

374
00:20:02,870 --> 00:20:03,400
So

375
00:20:03,620 --> 00:20:05,380
she had to finish the wedding ceremony

376
00:20:05,380 --> 00:20:06,680
and enter the bridal chamber

377
00:20:06,680 --> 00:20:07,450
before dark.

378
00:20:10,940 --> 00:20:14,080
She wants me to convey a message to Mr. Li.

379
00:20:15,770 --> 00:20:17,420
According to my Auntie's personality,

380
00:20:17,420 --> 00:20:18,330
she would say,

381
00:20:18,540 --> 00:20:19,600
"Do you regret it?"

382
00:20:19,700 --> 00:20:20,900
And then she would tell him,

383
00:20:20,900 --> 00:20:22,630
"It's useless to regret it now.

384
00:20:22,700 --> 00:20:24,840
I, He Xiaofeng, have a husband now.

385
00:20:24,940 --> 00:20:26,410
You can go wherever you want."

386
00:20:26,410 --> 00:20:28,010
You really know your Auntie.

387
00:20:28,110 --> 00:20:29,840
You're right about every word.

388
00:20:31,660 --> 00:20:32,720
By the way, Mother,

389
00:20:32,740 --> 00:20:35,000
-when I came back last night...
-That brat's done messing around outside

390
00:20:35,000 --> 00:20:36,000
and has come back?

391
00:20:41,610 --> 00:20:42,210
Master.

392
00:20:42,450 --> 00:20:43,850
Let me introduce him to you.

393
00:20:43,850 --> 00:20:44,490
This is

394
00:20:44,510 --> 00:20:46,750
Xiaobao's friend, Li Lianhua.

395
00:20:44,620 --> 00:20:46,170
[Fang Zeshi, Minister of the Ministry of Revenue]

396
00:20:47,460 --> 00:20:48,720
Greetings, Lord Fang.

397
00:20:52,510 --> 00:20:53,710
Look at you!

398
00:20:53,740 --> 00:20:55,540
You're frivolous and slovenly.

399
00:20:56,150 --> 00:20:58,210
Have you achieved anything outside?

400
00:20:58,680 --> 00:20:59,490
Today, I...

401
00:21:01,350 --> 00:21:02,570
What are you doing?

402
00:21:03,010 --> 00:21:03,570
Let go!

403
00:21:03,590 --> 00:21:05,390
-Let go of me.
-I'm sorry.

404
00:21:05,420 --> 00:21:06,110
Sorry.

405
00:21:06,380 --> 00:21:06,990
Lord Fang.

406
00:21:08,060 --> 00:21:10,120
I've never called you Father before.

407
00:21:10,900 --> 00:21:11,980
But in my heart,

408
00:21:13,120 --> 00:21:14,530
you're the best father.

409
00:21:21,410 --> 00:21:23,010
Did you get into

410
00:21:23,100 --> 00:21:24,620
some big trouble outside?

411
00:21:24,890 --> 00:21:27,460
You've been acting like a good boy since you came back.

412
00:21:27,460 --> 00:21:28,420
Listen,

413
00:21:29,150 --> 00:21:31,360
don't try to play tricks on me.

414
00:21:31,940 --> 00:21:32,440
Also,

415
00:21:32,820 --> 00:21:35,680
don't try to avoid your marriage with the princess.

416
00:21:35,700 --> 00:21:37,170
Now that your Auntie's wedding is over,

417
00:21:37,170 --> 00:21:38,730
it's your turn next.

418
00:21:39,150 --> 00:21:42,280
The emperor's grace is widely known. You can't avoid it.

419
00:21:42,430 --> 00:21:43,360
Look.

420
00:21:43,940 --> 00:21:45,750
-He's lecturing me again.
-You...

421
00:21:45,750 --> 00:21:47,860
I don't want to marry the princess. How many times have I told you?

422
00:21:47,860 --> 00:21:48,640
What kind of son

423
00:21:48,640 --> 00:21:49,810
talks to his father like this?

424
00:21:49,810 --> 00:21:51,740
You're stubborn and disobedient.

425
00:21:53,540 --> 00:21:54,220
Madam.

426
00:21:55,390 --> 00:21:56,120
Madam.

427
00:21:56,910 --> 00:21:58,320
Discipline your son.

428
00:21:58,640 --> 00:21:59,430
Alright.

429
00:22:00,420 --> 00:22:01,200
We have a guest here.

430
00:22:01,200 --> 00:22:02,330
Don't be too strict.

431
00:22:03,100 --> 00:22:03,700
By the way,

432
00:22:03,830 --> 00:22:04,640
the people from the Ministry of Works

433
00:22:04,640 --> 00:22:05,590
came to congratulate you.

434
00:22:05,590 --> 00:22:07,390
I've invited them to the Western Banquet Hall.

435
00:22:07,390 --> 00:22:08,950
Go and greet them.

436
00:22:10,620 --> 00:22:12,950
I'll leave your mother to discipline you.

437
00:22:16,420 --> 00:22:17,550
By the way, Xiaobao,

438
00:22:17,700 --> 00:22:18,380
Mr. Li,

439
00:22:19,700 --> 00:22:21,030
I have an urgent matter.

440
00:22:26,660 --> 00:22:28,060
Because of Xiaofeng's wedding,

441
00:22:28,060 --> 00:22:30,820
the Tianji Mountain Manor sent out wedding invitations a few days ago.

442
00:22:30,820 --> 00:22:33,820
We've received congratulatory gifts from friends from all sides in the past few days.

443
00:22:33,820 --> 00:22:35,820
I don't know who sent such a gift box.

444
00:22:36,910 --> 00:22:39,330
When I saw that it was the setting of the mechanism brocade box

445
00:22:39,330 --> 00:22:40,810
from our Tianji Hall before,

446
00:22:40,810 --> 00:22:42,140
it caught my attention.

447
00:22:42,490 --> 00:22:43,580
When I opened it,

448
00:22:43,820 --> 00:22:45,940
I found the Rama Heavenly Ice inside,

449
00:22:46,520 --> 00:22:48,300
just like the ice shard

450
00:22:48,320 --> 00:22:49,450
you asked me to keep.

451
00:22:55,900 --> 00:22:56,760
Why is it empty?

452
00:22:57,810 --> 00:22:58,590
How is that possible?

453
00:22:58,590 --> 00:22:59,920
It was in there just now.

454
00:23:01,290 --> 00:23:01,890
Master He.

455
00:23:02,380 --> 00:23:04,240
When did you see that the ice shard

456
00:23:04,480 --> 00:23:06,010
was still in the box before?

457
00:23:06,150 --> 00:23:07,370
About an hour ago.

458
00:23:07,700 --> 00:23:09,230
After seeing the ice shard,

459
00:23:09,350 --> 00:23:10,770
I found that the auspicious time had come,

460
00:23:10,770 --> 00:23:13,660
so I put the ice shard back into the box and locked it up.

461
00:23:13,660 --> 00:23:16,720
Then I sent the bride and groom into the bridal chamber after the ceremony.

462
00:23:16,720 --> 00:23:19,120
In the blink of an eye, it just disappeared.

463
00:23:19,180 --> 00:23:21,760
It seems that the person who took the ice shard had a clear goal

464
00:23:21,760 --> 00:23:22,820
and came prepared.

465
00:23:23,600 --> 00:23:26,300
There is only one way to the Tianji Mountain Manor.

466
00:23:26,300 --> 00:23:27,580
When we went up the mountain,

467
00:23:27,580 --> 00:23:29,330
we did not find anyone going down.

468
00:23:29,330 --> 00:23:30,700
The person who stole the Ice

469
00:23:30,700 --> 00:23:32,300
should still be in the Manor,

470
00:23:32,660 --> 00:23:34,390
perhaps just among the guests.

471
00:23:38,580 --> 00:23:40,210
Come on.

472
00:23:40,290 --> 00:23:40,750
Cheers.

473
00:23:41,940 --> 00:23:42,980
Thank you.

474
00:23:43,920 --> 00:23:44,530
Come on.

475
00:23:45,550 --> 00:23:46,010
Please.

476
00:23:52,540 --> 00:23:53,060
Cheers.

477
00:23:53,060 --> 00:23:54,460
There are so many guests.

478
00:23:54,500 --> 00:23:56,050
It's hard to find out who's suspicious

479
00:23:56,050 --> 00:23:57,740
just by staring at them like this.

480
00:23:57,740 --> 00:23:58,400
Master He.

481
00:23:58,980 --> 00:24:00,140
Have you arranged any performances

482
00:24:00,140 --> 00:24:01,600
for this wedding banquet?

483
00:24:02,050 --> 00:24:02,980
What do you mean?

484
00:24:03,740 --> 00:24:04,580
Since

485
00:24:04,950 --> 00:24:07,030
someone came here for the Ice,

486
00:24:07,390 --> 00:24:09,640
we might as well give him a surprise.

487
00:24:10,380 --> 00:24:11,110
You want to use the Rama Heavenly Ice

488
00:24:11,110 --> 00:24:12,550
I gave my mother before

489
00:24:12,960 --> 00:24:13,820
to lure him out?

490
00:24:14,810 --> 00:24:15,890
You're right.

491
00:24:16,220 --> 00:24:18,150
Not many people know about the Ice.

492
00:24:18,410 --> 00:24:19,560
If we show it to them,

493
00:24:19,830 --> 00:24:21,660
people who know about it and those who don't

494
00:24:21,660 --> 00:24:23,060
will react differently.

495
00:24:23,420 --> 00:24:24,500
Isn't it too risky?

496
00:24:25,300 --> 00:24:27,160
Don't let them take it away again.

497
00:24:27,230 --> 00:24:28,070
You brat.

498
00:24:28,460 --> 00:24:30,620
What kind of place do you think our own home is?

499
00:24:30,620 --> 00:24:31,900
I don't care who he is.

500
00:24:32,290 --> 00:24:34,570
It's not that easy

501
00:24:34,820 --> 00:24:36,480
to step out of the Tianji Hall.

502
00:24:37,640 --> 00:24:39,650
Thank you, Master He.

503
00:24:39,820 --> 00:24:40,300
Okay.

504
00:24:42,190 --> 00:24:42,920
Just in case,

505
00:24:43,440 --> 00:24:45,080
I'll go get Guardian Zhan.

506
00:24:51,060 --> 00:24:53,240
Who is this Guardian Zhan

507
00:24:53,750 --> 00:24:56,480
that needs your mother to invite him personally?

508
00:24:57,620 --> 00:24:59,300
He's just a weird guy.

509
00:25:00,060 --> 00:25:01,720
But his martial arts are quite impressive.

510
00:25:01,720 --> 00:25:03,920
My Auntie recruited him many years ago.

511
00:25:04,220 --> 00:25:05,820
He hasn't really talked to anyone

512
00:25:05,820 --> 00:25:07,680
except my Auntie all these years.

513
00:25:08,070 --> 00:25:10,330
You'll know when you get there. Let's go.

514
00:25:21,540 --> 00:25:22,400
Guardian Zhan.

515
00:25:22,980 --> 00:25:24,080
Don't stay up there.

516
00:25:24,080 --> 00:25:24,880
Come down now.

517
00:25:24,980 --> 00:25:25,780
My mother needs your help.

518
00:25:25,460 --> 00:25:27,600
[Zhan Yunfei, Dragon of the Martial Arts World]

519
00:25:28,700 --> 00:25:29,900
He's so arrogant.

520
00:25:30,900 --> 00:25:31,960
Just get used to it.

521
00:25:44,380 --> 00:25:45,700
Let me introduce you two.

522
00:25:45,700 --> 00:25:48,450
This is Physician Li, the master of the Lotus Tower.

523
00:25:48,450 --> 00:25:50,310
He's Fang Xiaobao's best friend.

524
00:25:50,710 --> 00:25:51,900
This is Guardian Zhan.

525
00:25:51,900 --> 00:25:53,490
He's known as the Dragon of the Martial Arts World,

526
00:25:53,490 --> 00:25:55,420
skilled in using the Wufeng Sword.

527
00:25:56,620 --> 00:25:57,480
Guardian Zhan.

528
00:25:57,820 --> 00:25:58,750
Nice to meet you.

529
00:25:59,460 --> 00:26:00,540
I'm Li Lianhua.

530
00:26:01,910 --> 00:26:02,840
I'm Zhan Yunfei.

531
00:26:12,060 --> 00:26:13,460
That's the general idea.

532
00:26:14,460 --> 00:26:16,830
We will take out a treasure to lure the thief out.

533
00:26:16,830 --> 00:26:18,630
To make sure nothing goes wrong,

534
00:26:18,980 --> 00:26:20,900
I need you to carefully arrange

535
00:26:21,220 --> 00:26:22,350
and guard the Manor.

536
00:26:22,380 --> 00:26:22,760
Okay.

537
00:26:25,370 --> 00:26:26,230
Guardian Zhan.

538
00:26:26,540 --> 00:26:27,980
I'm a little curious.

539
00:26:28,810 --> 00:26:29,450
With your

540
00:26:29,810 --> 00:26:31,210
excellent martial arts,

541
00:26:31,260 --> 00:26:34,260
why do you stay at the Tianji Mountain Manor as a guard?

542
00:26:39,840 --> 00:26:41,370
It's all my sister's fault.

543
00:26:41,740 --> 00:26:44,220
She made a bet with Guardian Zhan on a sword match.

544
00:26:44,220 --> 00:26:45,990
But Guardian Zhan lost unexpectedly,

545
00:26:45,990 --> 00:26:48,520
so he kept his promise and stayed at the Manor.

546
00:26:49,160 --> 00:26:49,930
A bet?

547
00:26:53,700 --> 00:26:56,500
You're known for your mastery of the Wufeng Sword.

548
00:26:56,910 --> 00:26:58,820
How could you lose to her?

549
00:26:59,080 --> 00:27:01,120
I was injured then, and I did lose.

550
00:27:01,610 --> 00:27:03,140
I was indebted for her help.

551
00:27:05,560 --> 00:27:06,620
I'll take my leave.

552
00:27:08,690 --> 00:27:12,550
[Tianji Mountain Manor]

553
00:27:14,400 --> 00:27:17,520
[Mysterious Lotus Casebook]

554
00:27:17,550 --> 00:27:18,870
[Ultimate Perfection]

555
00:27:18,210 --> 00:27:19,500
Everyone.

556
00:27:19,800 --> 00:27:22,440
Today is my sister's wedding day.

