00:41:01,400 --> 00:41:04,600
He had this tattoo on his back.

839
00:41:05,480 --> 00:41:06,490
My poor husband.

840
00:41:07,100 --> 00:41:08,300
On our wedding night,

841
00:41:08,930 --> 00:41:10,460
his body just disappeared.

842
00:41:10,900 --> 00:41:13,370
Only this bloody human skin was left.

843
00:41:13,990 --> 00:41:15,920
Dead or alive, there must be a body.

844
00:41:16,020 --> 00:41:17,680
The groom is not made of water.

845
00:41:17,940 --> 00:41:19,780
How could he just disappear?

846
00:41:20,570 --> 00:41:22,500
The bedding and clothes are intact

847
00:41:22,810 --> 00:41:24,330
and there are no signs of corrosion.

848
00:41:24,330 --> 00:41:26,590
It doesn't look like decomposing water.

849
00:41:26,720 --> 00:41:27,450
Ms. He,

850
00:41:28,100 --> 00:41:30,440
do you remember what happened last night?

851
00:41:31,560 --> 00:41:32,360
Last night?

852
00:41:33,200 --> 00:41:34,000
Last night...

853
00:41:34,210 --> 00:41:36,460
Calm down. Tell us slowly.

854
00:41:37,980 --> 00:41:39,110
Yesterday evening,

855
00:41:39,770 --> 00:41:41,370
after the wedding ceremony,

856
00:41:42,690 --> 00:41:44,620
he and I returned to the courtyard.

857
00:41:44,700 --> 00:41:46,430
Seeing that it was still early,

858
00:41:46,540 --> 00:41:49,000
we sat together in the courtyard for a while.

859
00:41:49,040 --> 00:41:52,410
We didn't go back to the room until the moon came out.

860
00:41:52,940 --> 00:41:55,140
After drinking the cross-cupped wine,

861
00:41:55,320 --> 00:41:56,930
I felt sleepy.

862
00:41:57,780 --> 00:42:00,020
He took me to bed to rest.

863
00:42:00,850 --> 00:42:02,980
I don't know what happened after that.

864
00:42:03,210 --> 00:42:04,010
When I woke up,

865
00:42:04,530 --> 00:42:06,170
I saw

866
00:42:06,610 --> 00:42:08,010
this bloody human skin.

867
00:42:09,370 --> 00:42:11,490
You felt sleepy after drinking the cross-cupped wine?

868
00:42:11,490 --> 00:42:12,090
Auntie.

869
00:42:12,690 --> 00:42:13,940
Think about it carefully.

870
00:42:13,940 --> 00:42:15,740
Was there anything suspicious?

871
00:42:18,560 --> 00:42:19,910
Anything suspicious?

872
00:42:30,910 --> 00:42:33,180
Leave one's mortal form behind and attain bliss,

873
00:42:33,180 --> 00:42:35,440
ascend to heaven and become immortal.

874
00:42:36,200 --> 00:42:39,840
I've never heard that he likes poetry.

875
00:42:40,270 --> 00:42:41,190
A poem.

876
00:42:49,480 --> 00:42:51,320
Poem, human skin.

877
00:42:52,580 --> 00:42:53,900
The pattern on the skin

878
00:42:54,360 --> 00:42:56,490
doesn't look like an ordinary tattoo.

879
00:42:56,790 --> 00:42:58,050
Does it mean anything?

880
00:42:58,580 --> 00:42:59,510
There seems to be

881
00:42:59,720 --> 00:43:01,450
something odd about the groom.

882
00:43:02,010 --> 00:43:02,900
Something odd?

883
00:43:11,500 --> 00:43:13,160
There are traces of fighting.

884
00:43:13,180 --> 00:43:15,100
Someone must have broken into the bridal chamber last night,

885
00:43:15,100 --> 00:43:16,520
but this person didn't hurt Auntie at all.

886
00:43:16,520 --> 00:43:17,780
What's certain is that

887
00:43:18,330 --> 00:43:19,370
no one else

888
00:43:19,580 --> 00:43:22,040
has been killed or attacked in the Tianji Mountain Manor.

889
00:43:22,040 --> 00:43:22,670
So,

890
00:43:22,980 --> 00:43:24,980
the murderer came for Wei Qingchou?

891
00:43:25,300 --> 00:43:26,420
He took the body away

892
00:43:26,420 --> 00:43:27,550
after he killed him?

893
00:43:27,770 --> 00:43:28,500
Impossible.

894
00:43:29,220 --> 00:43:31,140
Last night when I returned from delivering the treasure,

895
00:43:31,140 --> 00:43:32,140
the two of them

896
00:43:32,480 --> 00:43:34,280
gave me a box of wedding candies.

897
00:43:34,290 --> 00:43:37,520
No one else entered the bridal chamber after that.

898
00:43:38,340 --> 00:43:39,020
Otherwise,

899
00:43:39,300 --> 00:43:41,430
they could never escape my attention.

900
00:43:44,990 --> 00:43:46,630
That is to say, Wei Qingchou

901
00:43:47,090 --> 00:43:49,480
must have died after Brother Zhan returned.

902
00:43:49,480 --> 00:43:50,230
Brother Zhan

903
00:43:50,310 --> 00:43:53,820
has been guarding the opposite side of the house all night long.

904
00:43:53,820 --> 00:43:56,860
Then the murderer couldn't have entered or exited from the front.

905
00:43:56,860 --> 00:44:00,060
There is no entrance to the sill walls behind the windows.

906
00:44:00,180 --> 00:44:03,460
The mechanisms in the Tianji Hall have always been very famous.

907
00:44:03,460 --> 00:44:04,520
Is it possible that

908
00:44:05,660 --> 00:44:08,380
there are other mechanisms and secret passages here?

909
00:44:08,380 --> 00:44:09,300
This building

910
00:44:09,900 --> 00:44:11,460
is a very normal place,

911
00:44:11,900 --> 00:44:13,360
and there is nothing else.

912
00:44:13,560 --> 00:44:14,840
The body is gone,

913
00:44:15,140 --> 00:44:17,230
and the only thing left here is a tattooed human skin.

914
00:44:17,230 --> 00:44:19,100
If the murderer killed Wei Qingchou

915
00:44:19,100 --> 00:44:20,610
for this tattooed human skin,

916
00:44:20,610 --> 00:44:22,070
why didn't he take it away?

917
00:44:25,140 --> 00:44:25,650
Madam.

918
00:44:26,300 --> 00:44:27,940
Xiaofeng must be shocked.

919
00:44:28,540 --> 00:44:30,320
Why don't you take her to rest somewhere else?

920
00:44:30,320 --> 00:44:32,080
We can leave it to Xiaobao here.

921
00:44:33,110 --> 00:44:33,640
Alright.

922
00:44:34,660 --> 00:44:35,120
Li,

923
00:44:35,480 --> 00:44:36,620
you've been on standby outside the door

924
00:44:36,620 --> 00:44:37,830
since last night.

925
00:44:37,980 --> 00:44:38,980
Then stay here

926
00:44:39,540 --> 00:44:40,940
and listen to Young Master's orders.

927
00:44:40,940 --> 00:44:41,410
Yes.

928
00:44:42,360 --> 00:44:42,890
Let's go.

929
00:44:51,570 --> 00:44:52,830
What are you thinking?

930
00:44:54,140 --> 00:44:55,870
Since no one went out all night,

931
00:44:56,410 --> 00:44:57,810
the murderer and the body

932
00:44:58,980 --> 00:45:00,460
might not have left at all.

